<p>Daniel Ryan, or "dryan", is a senior frontend developer with the Obama 2012 campaign in Chicago, Illinois. Besides his campaign work, and releasing opensource projects like <a href="http://staging.dryan.com/css-smart-grid/">the CSS smart grids framework</a>, Daniel has been involved in the making of beautifully crafted websites such as <a href="http://webstandardssherpa.com/">Web Standards Sherpa</a> (designed by Dan Cederholm).</p>
<p>You can follow him on twitter <a href="http://twitter.com/#!/dryan">@dryan</a> and read his articles on <a href="http://dryan.com/">his website</a>.</p>